title: From What If To What Is
description:
What to do with “what if?” 

In “From What If To What Is,” Pastor Steven Furtick encourages us to stop worrying about what could be and start trusting who God is.

If you’ve just made a decision for Christ, please respond HERE: http://ele.vc/tIepfr

To support this ministry and help us continue to reach people all around the world click here: http://www.elevationchurch.org/giving/

Scripture References: 

Exodus 4, verses 1-5 

Numbers 13, verses 26-32
